    <text><!-- Double End-Point Attachment Method changed to Parallel Segmentation Method -->
        <body xml:id="uuid-fcc7ddd8-7e39-4032-ba3f-ba2dfc1f0eee">
            <div type="chapter" xml:id="sha-ham101">
                <p rend="centerautosum" xml:id="pa000001">Government of new <choice><abbr>Terr.</abbr><expan>Territory</expan></choice> of Nevada—Governor <name xml:id="_9" type="person">Nye</name>
                    <lb xml:id="_10"/> and the practical jokers—Mr. <name xml:id="_11" type="person">Clemens</name> begins journalistic life <lb xml:id="_12"/>on Virginia City <app from="dg0000" type="aet" xml:id="_13">
                        <lem xml:id="uuid-f3fc4683-b570-403f-ae10-3d976c8f4568">
                            <hi xml:id="uuid-98b78c33-a06c-4760-9f62-ff46166c8523" rend="italic">Enterprise</hi>
                        </lem>
                        <rdg xml:id="uuid-ee95a0c8-a4df-4a47-b957-c49613eab3f0" wit="#TS1 #TS2">Enterprise</rdg>
                    </app>—Reports legislative sessions—<lb xml:id="_14"/>He and <name xml:id="_15" type="person">Orion</name> prosper—<name xml:id="_16" type="person">Orion</name> builds <app from="dg0001" type="aet" xml:id="_17">
                        <lem xml:id="uuid-270b34bd-3b59-4a5c-935d-c4790682f1aa">twelve-thousand-dollar</lem>
                        <rdg xml:id="uuid-5a3e0774-13d5-45f2-ac87-08f98eb0341a" wit="#TS1">$12,000.</rdg>
                        <rdg xml:id="uuid-f662b333-0ff0-4b08-b1cf-aabb3ef37c58" wit="#TS2">$12,000</rdg>
                    </app> house—<app from="dg0002" type="aet" xml:id="_18">
                        <lem xml:id="uuid-54d08490-608c-402a-a0e3-4ddaab0be26c">Governor </lem>
                        <rdg xml:id="uuid-7c692127-56e0-4730-a978-f7e1d4ab697a" wit="#TS1 #TS2">Gov. </rdg>
                    </app>
                    <name xml:id="_19" type="person">Nye</name> turns Territory of <name xml:id="_20" type="place">Nevada</name> into a State. <app from="dg0003" type="aet" xml:id="_22">
                        <lem xml:id="uuid-cee18fca-11cc-4316-a0d6-55be002299bb"></lem>
                        <rdg xml:id="uuid-a9ee968e-1f5b-4bc6-907c-f18d141d61af" wit="#TS1 #TS2"><lb xml:id="uuid-913f9666-6549-4d6b-b499-f5275431e97b"/>(Miss <name xml:id="_24" type="person">Hobby</name>, please paste this in at this point, in record of April 1st, but I may not comment on it until later.)</rdg>
                    </app>
                </p>
                <p rend="center" xml:id="pa000002">
                    <hi xml:id="uuid-f391061f-7329-481f-8db8-ad1f42572a6f" rend="bold">PROMOTION FOR <name>BARNES</name>, <choice><orig>WHO</orig><reg>WHOM</reg></choice> <name>TILLMAN</name> BERATED</hi>
                    <ptr target="#en0001" type="an" xml:id="nv0001"/>
                </p>
                <milestone xml:id="uuid-b0ba1da0-4f9b-44af-b404-dd097eb2b284" rend="lightrule" unit="section"/>
                <p rend="text-indent:2" xml:id="pa000003">The appointment of <choice><corr>Barnes</corr><sic>Branes</sic></choice> to be Postmaster <app from="dg0005" type="aet" xml:id="ap0004">
                    <lem xml:id="uuid-db312f17-7f15-4041-99f7-6a96b3e60fba" wit="#TS1">so</lem>
                    <rdg xml:id="uuid-ea3d9d83-8371-48cb-b9c1-1eabaa8867eb" wit="#Times">so so</rdg>
                    <rdg xml:id="uuid-37300be1-2a22-4621-b292-e672fa264a5d" wit="#TS2">so</rdg>
                </app> soon after this incident has created endless talk here. It is taken to be the <rs type="person">President</rs>’s way of expressing confidence in <name xml:id="_23" type="person"><hi rend="bold">Barnes</hi></name> and repaying him for the pain he suffered as a result of the newspaper criticisms of his course.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
